## Initial Training Results

Model: YOLO11n

Epochs: 5

Preliminary Results:

- Precision: 86.0%
- Recall: 84.7%
- mAP50: 88.9%
- mAP50-95: 68.5%

These results demonstrate that the model is already capable of accurately detecting PPE equipment after a relatively short training period.

from PIL import Image
import matplotlib.pyplot as plt

img = Image.open("runs/detect/train/results.png")

plt.figure(figsize=(12,8))
plt.imshow(img)
plt.axis("off")
plt.show()
